successes.title: The Othermill: A Desktop CNC Mill for Everyone!
successes.description: With the Othermill, custom circuits, product prototypes, and other 3D objects are at your fingertips.

Pledges.description: BOOSTER - You receive our gratitude and a shout out on our website. Thank you!
SUPPORTER - You receive access to all our project models, plus a big high-five!
ADVOCATE - You receive a limited edition, extra hot Otherfab t-shirt.
ELECTRONICS KIT - Dive right in! You receive a great kit of everything you need to get started with surface mount soldering.
DEMO NIGHT - Learn how to use the Othermill from the experts, the folks who designed it. Class will be held at our shop in San Francisco.

WEARABLE ELECTRONICS! - Work with our engineers to make custom PCBs for awesome wearables projects. Bring clothes you want to light up and make beep. Materials Included. Class will be held at our shop in San Francisco
CATALYST - Be an adventurous early adopter! Get your Othermill first. Includes two bits to get you started. You also get a thumbdrive of 3D models to help you begin creating projects.
BUILDER - Get your Othermill early, be in the second batch made!  Includes two bits to get you started. You'll also get a thumbdrive of 3D models to help you begin creating projects.
FACILITATOR - An Othermill at our special introductory Kickstarter price. Includes two bits to get you started. In addition, you'll receive a thumbdrive of fun starter projects.

PIONEER - An Othermill with a starter kit of our favorite materials. Includes twenty non-toxic PCB board blanks, two machining wax blanks, and five birch plywood blanks - all sized specifically for your Othermill. Includes a selection of bits to get you started.

ELECTRONICS TINKERER - You receive an Othermill, everything that's in our basic electronics kit, plus a USB microscope! We'll set you up with some PCB board blanks and bits for the machine, so you can be making right out of the box.
CHAMPION - Customized Othermill with a backplate featuring your name or logo, plus a starter kit of materials. You will receive one of the first batch!
